title: Real Madrid Conquers El Clasico
description:
El Clasico postgame reaction from pitch-side at the Santiago Bernabeu following Real madrid's 3-1 win over Barcelona. The panel break down every aspect of the game, including Federico Valverde's brilliant performance, Robert Lewandowski's crucial misses and what Xavi got wrong in his lineup.
